 each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 13.847485, "shard": "07", "shelf_id": "sn86092282, 1921-01-06, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/wvu", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["west virginia", "beverly", "randolph", "united states"], "subject_headings": ["United States--West Virginia--Randolph--Beverly"], "subjects": [{"beverly": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:beverly&fo=json"}, {"randolph": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:randolph&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}, {"west virginia": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:west+virginia&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2025-07-16T10:49:12.853Z", "title": "Randolph enterprise (Beverly, W. Va.), January 6, 1921", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn86092282/1921-01-06/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86092282/"], "batch": ["wvu_eden_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1874", "description": ["Weekly Began in May, 1874. Cf. Bosworth, A.S. Hist. of Randolph Co., W. Va. -v. 82, no. 46 (Apr. 25, 1956). Published in Elkins, W. Va. by Oct. 7, 1903. First owner and editor was George P. Sargent. Editors: V.B. Trimble & T. Erwin Wells. Description based on: Vol. 3, no. 28 (Feb. 2, 1877). Randolph review (DLC)sn 86092283 Randolph enterprise-review (DLC)sn 86092284"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp