e-services/service/ndnp/wvu/batch_wvu_eden_ver01/data/sn86092282/00517011058/1921010601/0869.pdf", "segment_count": 8, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn86092282/1921-01-06/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "segment_id": "/service/ndnp/wvu/batch_wvu_eden_ver01/data/sn86092282/00517011058/1921010601/0869.xml", "segments": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn86092282/1921-01-06/ed-1/?sp=6"], "batch": ["wvu_eden_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "composite_location": ["0/united states/", "1/united states/west virginia/", "2/united states/west virginia/randolph/", "3/united states/west virginia/randolph/beverly/"], "contributor": ["west virginia university"], "date": "1921-01-06", "dates": ["1921-01-06"], "description": ["Greatest Religious Meeting in West Virginia BILLY SUNDAY Conducts a six weeks campaign atFaimonl beginning January 2nd Follow the meetings every day by reading THE FAIRMONT TIMES Which will cover the meetings with a special staff of writers Complete sermon the morning after it is delivered All the details of the campaign SPECIAL RATES payable in advance January 1 to March 1 Daily 2nionths 1 Daily and Sunday2months170 Idle Money Your idle funds can be earning 4 per cent interest while waiting investment if placed on deposit in our savings department We invite your special attention to our complete banking service both commercial and savings also qualified to act as Exe cutor Administrator etc Our facilities are at your disposal Davis Trust Co Elkins W Va We pay 4c interest on Savings Accounts Memler American Bankers Association what everyone wants It isto retain that appearance of natural sleep the simulation of life so that the visual memory will always remain sweeter It is for this that memory will always be associated with proper pro fessional service Z Kendall Sons Undertakers THE Old Year Has Passed and A New Year is Born Bom with a very very promising progress